title: Movie Review: Get Out
description:
Welcome to episode 89 of Sleep and Relax ASMR! Today I will be whispering my analysis and review on the 2017 thriller "Get Out," directed by Jordan Peele. What did you guys think about the film? Let me know by getting in touch with the show, and enjoy the episode! 

Visit our website: www.SleepandRelaxASMR.com to get updates and access to special promos on awesome brands!
